NAME
    Sys::Manage - Systems management commands/scripts environment

DESCRIPTION
    Sys::Manage::Cmd - Systems management command volley

    Sys::Manage::Conn - Connection to remote Perl

    Sys::Manage::Schedule - Scriptic schedule trunk

    See particular modules.

LICENSE
    This is free software; you can use redistribute it and/or modify it
    under the same terms as Perl itself.

AUTHOR
    Andrew V Makarow <makarow at mail.com>
	
PREREQUISITES
    Currently implemented and tested on Win32 Active Perl 5.6.

HOW TO BUILD AND INSTALL

    Type:
	
	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make install
    Or:
	copy ./lib/Sys/* into perl/site/lib/Sys

    See examples, which should be configured and installed manually.
